name: Rp-1 Multi-Effects Processor
details:
stereo multi-effects processor24 effects, up to 10 at a time.
Advanced speaker simulator.
Full MIDI input and output mapping.
Fully programmable local and global continuous controller assignments.
Programmable effects loop for outboard gear.
Stereo headphone output.
Can be used as a remote MIDI footswitch controller for all MIDI controllable devices.
